            <p class="subtitle">Your Gateway to Smart Learning and Seamless Classroom Booking</p>
            <p class="description">"Connecting Students, Faculty, and Administrators through an intelligent classroom scheduling system."</p>
            <a href="login" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>

